ounded in 1983 and is based in Noida, India.", "fullTimeEmployees": 7619, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Ashok Kumar Chaturvedi B.Sc.", "age": 69, "title": "Executive Chairman & MD", "yearBorn": 1956, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 156449000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Jeevaraj Gopal Pillai", "age": 64, "title": "Whole-Time Director, Director of Sustainability & President of Flexi. Pack. and New Prod. Devl.", "yearBorn": 1961, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 17878000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Apoorvshree  Chaturvedi", "title": "Director of Global Operations", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. H. M. Raje M.Chem.Engg.", "age": 69, "title": "Vice President of Technology", "yearBorn": 1956, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Surajit  Pal", "title": "Vice President of Investor Relations", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Dinesh  Jain B.Sc. LLB, DBA, LLM", "age": 71, "title": "President of Legal & Corporate Affairs", "yearBorn": 1954, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Ritesh  Chaudhry", "title": "Senior Vice President of Secretarial, Company Secretary & Compliance Officer", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Anant Pal Singh B.Pharma", "age": 78, "title": "President of Group Coordination & Marketing", "yearBorn": 1947, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Chandan  Chattaraj B.Com, Pgdm(Ir&Pm)", "age": 61, "title": "President of Human Resources - India & Global", "yearBorn": 1964, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Subhash  Khatua", "title": "Deputy General Manager of Secre